WEBVTT

00:03.621 --> 00:05.828
A look can say a lot.

00:08.085 --> 00:11.409
A look can be honest and true.

00:13.281 --> 00:14.826
A look can speak for you,...

00:16.839 --> 00:20.727
...say what's on your mind or in your heart.

00:24.069 --> 00:28.411
A look can say what's best unsaid, and find the right words...

00:30.906 --> 00:32.885
...without having to say a word.

00:36.359 --> 00:37.257
A look...

00:41.533 --> 00:42.477
It's great to see you.

00:44.049 --> 00:45.325
...can say a lot.

